{"tid":1100662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「學動」臨終怨言另起爐灶 聲稱學生為主組織難有作用","createTime":"2019-04-10T14:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T15:19:16.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"31360e13f9c179267934a9352eea6674a62d7951","tid":1100662,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/0406/272514.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232109%2F2019%2F0406%2F272514.html&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTkyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=e4cb6076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2019/0406/272514.html</a><br />\n<br />\n搞「港獨」搞到窮途末路的「學生動源」，昨日在facebook貼了個所謂成立三周年的宣言，其內容似是臨終怨言。內容稱，「學生動源」過去三年堅信香港獨立才是香港以及香港民族的唯一生路，但「港獨」勢力陷入低潮，香港情況一年比一年嚴峻，而基本法23條立法亦事在必行雲雲。「學生動源」又稱，以學生為主體的政治團體難以繼續發揮有效作用，「經過學生動源成員慎重地考慮後決定，學生動源將會於短期內另組主張香港獨立之政團，廣納不同年齡層人士繼續為香港民族共同奮鬥」，諸如此類。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n  事實上，《大公報》早前已踢爆「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林將會另立「港獨」組織，什麼學生團體難以發揮作用，根本是謊言。實情就是荒廢學業的鍾翰林即將面對失學，卻又不想努力工作，於是多番往來台灣，「獨鴛鴦」林保華、楊月清耳提面命指點鍾翰林。[red]</span>上月有讀者向《大公報》提供獨家相片，證明鍾翰林悄悄地與「獨鴛鴦」進入銀行處理一些錢銀事務。<span style=\"color: red;\">由此推斷，所謂新的「港獨」組織不過是廢青鍾翰林為了個人上位、呃錢溝女的產物。等到錢用光了，鍾同學還會再搞個「新名堂」出來，延續廢青的寄生蟲生活。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「新名堂」出來，延續廢青的寄生蟲生活。"},{"pid":"2851b7b2a29f2c79f5a344bdc9e74bf0afa3eb1f","tid":1100662,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65bc28d7c3bac653ac9f64b2905a858b8f30d19","tid":1100662,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8972310316dae81c63a30aa027a74786181e98","tid":1100662,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"大公報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1b510e077fb098720f04893f29031deb83bc0e","tid":1100662,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"泛民+本土=<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/21590658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F21590658.jpg&h=14a35412&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bab429e7a8ff0cd9118dc23b810cf20b2bb800b","tid":1100662,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad1b510e077fb098720f04893f29031deb83bc0e","tid":1100662,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"泛民+本土=<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/21590658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F21590658.jpg&h=14a35412&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"而家講獨派又內戰，kk，關sir率領抄登仔大戰仇阿達，貓靈做大佬反而唔敢出聲又唔幫關sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89956031d6adc0e8dcefb9ab21f1426b55f51e4","tid":1100662,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bab429e7a8ff0cd9118dc23b810cf20b2bb800b","tid":1100662,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad1b510e077fb098720f04893f29031deb83bc0e","tid":1100662,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:48:15.000Z","msg":"泛民+本土=<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/21590658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F21590658.jpg&h=14a35412&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"而家講獨派又內戰，kk，關sir率領抄登仔大戰仇阿達，貓靈做大佬反而唔敢出聲又唔幫關sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:06:20.00